    <string name="etrto_info_text" tools:ignore="Typos"><![CDATA[The ETRTO size defines the exact tire and rim geometry.<br><br>
            Example: 40 622 19<br>
            • 40  - tire width in mm<br>
            • 622 - rim diameter in mm<br>
            • 19  - rim inner width in mm<br><br>
            Read these numbers directly from the tire sidewall and rim.
